description: After creating a backup you can restore the information at a later time. Choose the Restore... option and browse to the file location to restore the file.
NOTE: Enpass Technologies replaced WALLETX files with .ENPASSBACKUP files when it released version 6 of Enpass.

common_filenames.description: Enpass_Backup_2016_01_01_16-30-09.walletx - Example name of a backup, which includes the date and timestamp when the file was created.
